                        <li>Lots of money to spend here</li>
                        <li>Leave worries home </li>
                        <li>And always return to PEru</li>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="main-content-right ">
                    <div class="main-content-right-container ">
                        <span>Latest Posts</span>

                        <li>How to get to Machu Picchu</li>
                        <li>Handling the heights </li>
                        <li>Chewing CoCa leaves</li>
                        <li>Lots of money to spend here</li>
                        <li>Leave worries home </li>
                        <li>And always return to PEru</li>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Comments section -->

        </div>
    </div>
</main>